Author: eren0x
Title: [LAUNCHED] ⚽ Bethereum - Blockchain-powered social betting! 🚀
Body: Gamification elements, an easy-to-understand interface and simplicity in account creation and management distinguish Bethereum from other betting platforms. We use Ethereum technology to deliver the most common demands from sports betting, such as instant payouts, unlimited winnings and transparency in fund management. However, Bethereum is much more than just sports betting. In addition to limitless scalability, the platform can also handle additional items such as eSports, fantasy sports and casino-type games. We will also include a tool kit for developers and white-label customers, complete with a graphic Smart Contract builder to further expand the use of our platform. At the core of the platform is the Bether token, which will be used for all interactions. The initial token sale will distribute 1 billion tokens and the proceeds of these funds will be used to expand Bethereum, in addition to paying for operating costs.
